description: Returns information about the most recent high availability monitoring test that was performed on the host in a cluster. If a test isn't performed, the status and start time in the response would be null.

parameters.name: GatewayARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the gateway. Use the  ListGateways operation to return a list of gateways for your account and Amazon Web Services Region.

nested_items.name: GatewayARN
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the gateway. Use the  ListGateways operation to return a list of gateways for your account and Amazon Web Services Region.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the high availability monitoring test. If a test hasn't been performed, the value of this field is null.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The time the high availability monitoring test was started. If a test hasn't been performed, the value of this field is null.
